{"tid":956723,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[一発ツモ]召集日本麻雀同好","createTime":"2018-12-26T13:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T03:48:11.000Z","uid":22422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"66e34575e76018688b1faf79906ceb93422679d5","tid":956723,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"歡迎玩厭港式麻雀嘅人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皆んな、マージャングループへようこそ。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本麻雀玩法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/日本麻雀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%BA%BB%E9%9B%80&d=pJzRYsdkl93uV2yzkgrKUaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6bf9d799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/日本麻雀</a><br />\n<br />\n最常見嘅日本麻雀網上對戰系統：天鳳<br />\n<a href=\"http://tenhou.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftenhou.net&d=pJzRYsdkl93uV2yzkgrKUaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3519338d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tenhou.net</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講 日本麻雀一番起糊（ドラ唔算係坐底嘅一番）<br />\n最後牌山會剩十四隻唔會喺呢局摸到嘅牌<br />\n牌路冇香港牌咁窄 <br />\n未必需要扣牌扣到完場<br />\n而且食糊個規矩係有振聽規則<br />\n所以打一隻牌都需要比香港牌更謹慎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e73bb1b1e8b009b12f9cc8de40c424301d386e","tid":956723,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e34575e76018688b1faf79906ceb93422679d5","tid":956723,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"歡迎玩厭港式麻雀嘅人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皆んな、マージャングループへようこそ。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本麻雀玩法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/日本麻雀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%BA%BB%E9%9B%80&d=pJzRYsdkl